    dc:description "Figure 13. Solanum furcatum Dunal A Habit B Detail flower (A-B Anonymous s. n., grown from seed sent by J. Edmonds, originally from California [ADW 42421]). Drawing by M. L. Szent-Ivany, first published in Symon (1981), courtesy of the Board of the Botanic Gardens and State Herbarium (Adelaide, South Australia), reproduced with permission." ;
