    dc:description "Figure 14. Solanum furcatum Dunal A Habit B Flowering branch C Infrutescence with developing fruits. D Fully mature fruit dropping off with pedicel (A-D Knapp s. n., United States of America, California, San Francisco, Golden Gate Park, in front of California Academy of Sciences, 11 June 2013). Photos by S. Knapp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/218717" ;
